Xin lỗi về tình huống khó khăn mà bạn đang gặp phải. Tôi ở đây để lắng nghe và hỗ trợ bạn. Hãy chia sẻ với tôi về vấn đề bạn đang phải đối mặt để chúng ta có thể tìm cách giải quyết nó.

I'm feeling really anxious lately and I don't know why.

It's understandable to feel anxious without knowing the exact cause. Sometimes anxiety can be triggered by a variety of factors such as stress, past traumas, or even imbalances in brain chemistry. Have there been any major changes or events in your life recently that could be contributing to your anxiety? It might also be helpful to identify any negative thought patterns or behaviors that could be perpetuating your anxiety. Would you like to explore this further?
